Given the following program and the variable in complex data type, decompose the it into variables with primary data type.. The program is int fn2(int p1_int, int p2_int) { return p1_int - p2_int; }
int k;
int l;
int fn3(p1_int) {
  int o;
  for (k = 0; k >= -27; k = k - 6)
    for (l = 0; l < 5; l++)
      p1_int = fn2(o, p1_int);
  return p1_int;
}
int main() {}
.                 The target to be optimized is `k` (declared in `fn3` as `int k;`).
